PrecisAppointment of MARIE SENÉCAL-TREMBLAY, of Montreal, Quebec, as Vice-chairperson of the Canadian Artists and Producers Professional Relations Tribunal, on a part-time basis, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of two years, effective April 1, 2002.
